IN A YELLOW BOAT 
A YELLOW BOAT

628
00:21:46,638 --> 00:21:49,057
IN A YELLOW BOAT.

629
00:21:49,057 --> 00:21:51,518
WE'RE MAKING A STAND 
WE'RE TAKING A STAND--

630
00:21:51,518 --> 00:21:52,769
IN A YELLOW BOAT 
A YELLOW BOAT

631
